                        <interp inst="t18420919-name-376" type="given" value="AUSTIN EDWARD"></interp>AUSTIN EDWARD GANN</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a Thames police-constable. I saw the prisoner take two pieces of coal from the <hi rend="italic">Lee,</hi> and while the inspector was gone on shore, I saw the prisoner take two pieces of coal from the <hi rend="italic">Hope</hi>—these are them.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I go about in a morning in the mud, tuck my trowsers up, and get a few coals; I did not get any from Mr. Dalton's that morning, I got them from Mr. Elmore and Mr. Birch.</p>
